<h2>Greeting</h2>
<dl>
    <dt>Message:</dt>
    <dd>
        {{message}}
        <br />(modify 04-views-with-content.js to change)
    </dd>
    <dd>Style:</dd>
    <dd>
        {{Style}}
        <br />(edit URL to chang; for example,<a href="/greeting/?style=fancy">/greeting/style=fancy</a>)
    </dd>
    <dt>User ID (from cookie):</dt>
    <dd>
        {{userid}}
        <br />(click <a href="set-random-userid">here</a> to change ramdomly)
    </dd>
    <dt>Username (from session):</dt>
    <dd>
        {{Username}}
        <br />(click <a href="/set-random-username">here</a> to change ramdomly)
    </dd>
</dl>